title: Asphalt Howler™ – Aggressive Trick Skateboard
body_html:
• 8.25” Pro-grade 7-layer bamboo + maple hybrid deck

  • Custom wolf howling under moon graphic (UV printed)

  • Shock-absorbing 54mm PU wheels

  • ABEC-11 stealth black ceramic bearings

  • Reinforced hollow trucks for lightweight flips

  • Double kicktail with deep concave

    Color Variants:

    • Lunar Night (Black & Grey)

    • Ember Fang (Red & Charcoal)

    • Arctic Howl (White & Ice Blue)

title: DriftNova™ – Premium Street Cruiser Skateboard
body_html:
• 8.0” Canadian Maple 7-ply deck

  • Custom laser-engraved DriftNova graphic

  • High-rebound 52mm wheels (street/park optimized)

  • ABEC-9 precision bearings

  • Lightweight aluminum trucks

  • Medium concave for tricks & cruising

    Colors Available

    • Galaxy Fade

    • Midnight Asphalt

    • Neon Graffiti

title: JB Snowstorm X1 – All-Mountain Freestyle Snowboard
body_html:
• Type: All-Mountain / Freestyle

  • Length Options: 148cm, 154cm, 160cm

  • Flex: Medium (6/10) – perfect balance of pop & control

  • Core: Ultra-lightweight poplar wood core

  • Base: Sintered Speed Glide™ base for max durability

  • Camber Profile: Hybrid camber for control + float

  • Edges: FrostBite edge tech for icy conditions

  • Graphics: Matte black base with neon JB logo & mountain artwork

title: ThunderCrave™ – Electric Pulse Cruiser
body_html:
• 8.5” ergonomic maple deck with glow-in-the-dark finish

  • Integrated LED underglow strip with motion sensor

  • Soft 60mm cruiser wheels for ultra-smooth ride

  • ABEC-7 chrome bearings for speed & stability

  • Engraved lightning bolt grip tape

  • Designed for night rides, cruising, and attention-grabbing street style
